WEBVTT

00:00:32.261 --> 00:00:35.097
THE JUDGE RETURNS

00:01:29.193 --> 00:01:30.194
How is it?

00:01:30.820 --> 00:01:33.531
To have returned to a world you wanted
in your past life?

00:02:22.872 --> 00:02:25.124
Choi Yun-sun,
the Minister of Land and Transport?

00:02:25.207 --> 00:02:29.128
I'll make sure homes are no longer bought
solely for speculation.

00:02:29.587 --> 00:02:33.591
As long as I, Choi Yun-sun,
am the Minister of Land and Transport

00:02:34.175 --> 00:02:37.928
the green belt will not be harmed
without permission.

00:02:38.721 --> 00:02:40.723
Until the day I resign

00:02:40.806 --> 00:02:44.226
I vow to be a public servant

00:02:44.310 --> 00:02:46.479
who causes no shame.

00:02:49.482 --> 00:02:53.152
She'll join us from today.

00:02:56.822 --> 00:02:59.950
NEW CITY PLANNING FOR HANYANG
AND CLEARING OF THE GREEN BELT IN 2027

00:03:00.034 --> 00:03:01.368
MINISTRY OF LAND AND TRANSPORT

00:03:10.044 --> 00:03:13.005
I can't believe she's leaking
a public project like this!

00:03:13.380 --> 00:03:17.426
The government will make
an official announcement next fall.

00:03:17.510 --> 00:03:19.386
The Presidential election is before that.

00:03:20.095 --> 00:03:23.182
Will this plan go forward,
even with a new President?

00:03:25.017 --> 00:03:28.604
It doesn't matter who the President is.

00:03:28.687 --> 00:03:30.815
The true President of Korea is here

00:03:31.232 --> 00:03:32.858
at Suojae, after all.

00:03:36.612 --> 00:03:37.988
Come on. What are you doing?

00:03:38.072 --> 00:03:41.784
Our Minister of Land and Transport brought
an amazing gift for us.

00:03:41.867 --> 00:03:44.662
We have to build condos, bridges

00:03:44.745 --> 00:03:46.247
and buildings, you know?

00:03:46.330 --> 00:03:47.414
A round of applause!

00:03:56.382 --> 00:03:58.050
And everyone, take your bags.

00:03:58.133 --> 00:03:59.134
Go ahead.

00:04:01.262 --> 00:04:02.388
Hold on.

00:04:02.888 --> 00:04:05.599
This is Mr. Kang. Say hi.

00:04:08.227 --> 00:04:09.937
Help her out when she needs.

00:04:10.855 --> 00:04:12.940
Sin-jin and Gwang-to.

00:04:13.023 --> 00:04:14.859
I must stop both of them

00:04:14.942 --> 00:04:17.403
or the country's justice
will be gone for good.

00:04:20.739 --> 00:04:22.741
EPISODE 11

00:04:22.825 --> 00:04:24.535
All the special activity funds from today

00:04:25.536 --> 00:04:27.496
will be invested into Hanyang City.

00:04:27.580 --> 00:04:28.831
Yes, which is why

00:04:28.914 --> 00:04:33.711
I've told all conglomerate executives
to prepare money for the campaign.

00:04:34.837 --> 00:04:35.963
Is that enough?

00:04:37.339 --> 00:04:39.884
Whatever the excuse

00:04:40.384 --> 00:04:43.679
talk to the President's office
to draw up the supplementary budget.

00:04:44.346 --> 00:04:45.556
Well...

00:04:46.599 --> 00:04:50.185
the opposition is waiting to strike
with a special activity funds audit.

00:04:50.269 --> 00:04:51.979
It's not as easy as it sounds.

00:04:52.396 --> 00:04:54.899
How can you handle an election
if you're so scared?

00:04:55.357 --> 00:04:58.110
Increase the budget
for the special activity fund.

00:04:59.194 --> 00:05:00.779
When the proposal reaches the assembly

00:05:00.863 --> 00:05:02.948
just offer the opposition something
in return.

00:05:03.032 --> 00:05:06.368
Don't let them decrease
a penny of the special activity fund.

00:05:06.452 --> 00:05:07.620
Do you understand?

00:05:08.829 --> 00:05:09.830
Yes, Mr. President.

00:05:13.250 --> 00:05:16.420
I let you be the party leader.
It's about time you get to work.

00:05:17.087 --> 00:05:18.130
I apologize.

00:05:20.382 --> 00:05:21.383
You can go.

00:05:51.038 --> 00:05:52.039
Have a seat.

00:06:03.676 --> 00:06:05.511
Does Your Young Honor realize

00:06:06.428 --> 00:06:08.931
where he is right now?

00:06:13.602 --> 00:06:14.687
Look at that.

00:06:16.897 --> 00:06:20.150
You had the chance
to become the Chief Justice

00:06:20.526 --> 00:06:22.194
yet you couldn't even watch your son.

00:06:23.278 --> 00:06:24.613
I apologize.

00:06:25.698 --> 00:06:27.741
In fact, I've come here

00:06:28.784 --> 00:06:30.744
to talk to you about that.

00:06:31.370 --> 00:06:33.497
You're retired now.
What more is there to say?

00:06:34.540 --> 00:06:36.917
This was 15 years ago

00:06:38.002 --> 00:06:39.461
but I colluded with S Construction

00:06:39.545 --> 00:06:42.381
and framed an evicted resident
as a victim.

00:06:42.464 --> 00:06:44.550
Are you here for a confessional?

00:06:44.633 --> 00:06:46.593
Because that's for a priest, not me.

00:06:47.052 --> 00:06:48.137
But

00:06:48.679 --> 00:06:51.306
the child of that evictee

00:06:52.016 --> 00:06:53.475
became a judge.

00:06:55.978 --> 00:06:57.021
What?

00:06:58.313 --> 00:07:00.190
It's all because of that very judge

00:07:00.274 --> 00:07:03.444
that my son suddenly confessed,
leading me to resign.

00:07:05.612 --> 00:07:07.906
So, who is that?

00:07:10.075 --> 00:07:12.202
Judge Lee Han-young

00:07:12.870 --> 00:07:14.455
under Sin-jin.

00:07:15.205 --> 00:07:16.623
Mr. Kang told me

00:07:16.707 --> 00:07:18.834
this was where people really worked
for the nation.

00:07:20.377 --> 00:07:23.422
I'd like to contribute
to the work for the nation.

00:07:31.221 --> 00:07:33.474
Judge Lee, who'd returned for revenge was

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:36.727
more manipulative than a snake
and without mercy.

00:07:36.810 --> 00:07:39.354
If Sin-jin ever brings him to you

00:07:39.438 --> 00:07:40.522
do not trust him

00:07:41.648 --> 00:07:43.275
no matter what.

00:07:44.026 --> 00:07:47.071
A rookie judge made a Justice resign

00:07:47.780 --> 00:07:48.781
and Sin-jin is

00:07:49.907 --> 00:07:51.116
behind all that?

00:07:51.575 --> 00:07:54.369
I'd like to suggest
Justice Hwang Nam-yong.

00:07:57.748 --> 00:08:00.959
But he recommended Nam-yong to my face.

00:08:04.755 --> 00:08:05.881
What is he

00:08:07.007 --> 00:08:08.217
trying to pull here?

00:08:16.058 --> 00:08:19.478
We built Suojae as the shadow government
before the end of Mr. Park's term.

00:08:21.230 --> 00:08:22.231
How does it feel?

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:25.818
To have seen the real powerhouse of Korea.

00:08:30.197 --> 00:08:31.448
It was thrilling.

00:08:32.449 --> 00:08:33.450
"Thrilling"?

00:08:35.369 --> 00:08:36.370
Interesting.

00:08:38.205 --> 00:08:40.290
I guess I was like you, too.

00:08:42.126 --> 00:08:43.335
I have a question.

00:08:45.087 --> 00:08:47.798
Why did you take me there?

00:08:50.217 --> 00:08:52.302
Are you asking if I trust you that much?

00:08:55.222 --> 00:08:56.223
No.

00:08:57.975 --> 00:08:59.977
I didn't bring you there
because I trusted you.

00:09:01.019 --> 00:09:02.771
I brought you there so you'd trust me.

00:09:03.230 --> 00:09:05.232
This is real power.

00:09:06.358 --> 00:09:08.443
So, trust and follow my lead.

00:09:11.029 --> 00:09:13.740
The Minister of Land and Transport leaked
a government proposal

00:09:14.116 --> 00:09:17.327
which the leader of Suojae is using
to embezzle public funds.

00:09:17.411 --> 00:09:20.914
Suojae has become an ugly cartel
of power and money.

00:09:22.416 --> 00:09:25.210
I'll get rid of Gwang-to,
the crazy shaman believer

00:09:25.294 --> 00:09:27.212
and become the leader of Suojae.

00:09:28.922 --> 00:09:30.465
When the day comes

00:09:31.967 --> 00:09:34.678
I'll need someone to establish
new justice with me.

00:09:37.139 --> 00:09:38.265
Someone

00:09:39.516 --> 00:09:41.727
who will never betray me.

00:10:08.962 --> 00:10:10.297
What is justice

00:10:13.091 --> 00:10:14.635
to you?

00:10:25.479 --> 00:10:27.397
The devil works quickly and clearly.

00:10:27.481 --> 00:10:29.066
Nothing ever hinders it.

00:10:29.524 --> 00:10:31.860
But justice needs formality
and a proper procedure.

00:10:32.986 --> 00:10:35.197
So, it feels lazy, slow

00:10:35.822 --> 00:10:36.990
and delayed.

00:10:37.866 --> 00:10:39.451
The justice that I want

00:10:39.534 --> 00:10:41.787
works clearly and quicker than the devil.

00:10:41.870 --> 00:10:43.497
And it can't be hindered by anything.

00:10:46.083 --> 00:10:47.542
What does justice mean to you?

00:10:55.384 --> 00:10:59.346
Are you sure you made a fair judgment?

00:10:59.429 --> 00:11:00.430
Yes.

00:11:03.183 --> 00:11:04.268
No.

00:11:05.310 --> 00:11:07.938
There's no point in asking you this.

00:11:08.981 --> 00:11:10.857
Anyone would know it in their hearts.

00:11:16.196 --> 00:11:17.906
To me, justice is

00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:22.286
not something found
through questions and debates.

00:11:23.328 --> 00:11:25.789
It's equity

00:11:26.623 --> 00:11:27.833
and common sense

00:11:28.917 --> 00:11:30.294
everyone knows in their hearts.

00:11:35.590 --> 00:11:38.885
Equity and common sense
that everyone knows in their hearts?

00:11:43.223 --> 00:11:45.475
It aligns with my definition in some ways.

00:11:48.979 --> 00:11:49.980
No.

00:11:51.148 --> 00:11:52.816
To you, justice is

00:11:53.692 --> 00:11:54.735
self-righteousness.

00:12:09.291 --> 00:12:11.418
Who's the lady you came with
the last time?

00:12:11.501 --> 00:12:12.711
She was so pretty.

00:12:12.794 --> 00:12:14.629
Pretty? Who was it?

00:12:14.713 --> 00:12:16.590
I came with Ms. Yu from Haenal Law Firm.

00:12:19.384 --> 00:12:22.220
Are you planning your wedding
now that you've given Mr. Eom

00:12:22.512 --> 00:12:23.722
as your sacrifice to Haenal?

00:12:24.556 --> 00:12:25.682
No, it's too soon.

00:12:25.766 --> 00:12:27.184
Come on.

00:12:27.267 --> 00:12:28.935
You mixed her jjajangmyeon

00:12:29.019 --> 00:12:32.230
and tied her apron for her.
You have to marry her!

00:12:32.606 --> 00:12:36.234
It's cowardly for a man not to marry her
after all that flirting!

00:12:36.318 --> 00:12:37.694
I just...

00:12:37.778 --> 00:12:40.572
You tied her apron for her?
You're basically married.

00:12:42.032 --> 00:12:43.075
Right.

00:12:43.575 --> 00:12:46.661
The lady was looking at you
with so much love.

00:12:49.122 --> 00:12:50.665
Enjoy your dinner.

00:12:56.963 --> 00:12:59.216
I didn't know you were a coward.

00:12:59.299 --> 00:13:00.342
Me?

00:13:01.468 --> 00:13:02.469
Bottoms-up.

00:13:03.011 --> 00:13:05.222
Don't be a coward and leave any.

00:13:16.691 --> 00:13:17.692
One more glass?

00:13:24.699 --> 00:13:28.036
SEOUL CENTRAL DISTRICT COURT

00:13:32.165 --> 00:13:33.208
Did you check it?

00:13:35.919 --> 00:13:36.920
We'll know soon enough.

00:13:37.003 --> 00:13:39.381
It's 30 million won
from Sarang Securities, correct?

00:13:39.464 --> 00:13:41.091
Tae-sik's illegal loans were exposed

00:13:41.174 --> 00:13:43.093
with the arrest of the loan officer

00:13:43.176 --> 00:13:46.221
at the Jeongdaun Savings Bank
for embezzlement.

00:13:47.305 --> 00:13:49.933
It won't be easy to get an arrest warrant
for Tae-sik.

00:13:50.392 --> 00:13:52.686
The higher-ups will do anything
to stop me.

00:13:53.395 --> 00:13:54.396
30 million won...

00:13:54.563 --> 00:13:56.690
Why do you need a warrant?
You know your expertise.

00:13:56.773 --> 00:13:57.816
What?

00:13:58.108 --> 00:13:59.109
An emergency arrest?

00:13:59.192 --> 00:14:00.735
Break Tae-sik's back first.

00:14:00.819 --> 00:14:02.279
I'll twist his neck.

00:14:04.239 --> 00:14:05.949
So, I have to do all the work.

00:14:06.032 --> 00:14:09.161
Don't you know Tae-sik's neck is guarded
by Sin-jin?

00:14:09.244 --> 00:14:10.829
It'll be harder to twist his neck.

00:14:10.912 --> 00:14:12.497
Okay, fine.

00:14:13.290 --> 00:14:15.083
Be ready to twist his neck any moment.

00:14:15.167 --> 00:14:16.293
Don't worry.

00:14:17.210 --> 00:14:19.045
I'll be sure to warm up.

00:14:26.470 --> 00:14:30.265
Mr. Han Gwang-hun, the loan officer
at Jeongdaun Savings Bank.

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:31.641
Yes.

00:14:33.685 --> 00:14:35.896
You invested 150 million won
using embezzled money

00:14:35.979 --> 00:14:38.356
until just last month.

00:14:38.982 --> 00:14:40.650
I'm sorry.

00:14:40.734 --> 00:14:43.028
I'll do everything to return the money.

00:14:43.111 --> 00:14:45.697
No need. You didn't steal my money.

00:14:46.781 --> 00:14:47.782
Sorry?

00:14:48.575 --> 00:14:51.745
You were going to return the money
once the stock prices went up, anyway.

00:14:52.996 --> 00:14:54.998
- Aren't I right?
- Sorry?

00:14:57.417 --> 00:15:00.003
Oh, yeah, that's right.

00:15:01.838 --> 00:15:05.091
What a convincing, honest confession.

00:15:05.550 --> 00:15:07.344
It's like you're making a confessional.

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:11.848
That being said

00:15:13.517 --> 00:15:15.435
help me serve our country.

00:15:16.520 --> 00:15:17.521
Be a buddy.

00:15:22.484 --> 00:15:23.902
TESTIMONY BY KIM SEOK-TAE

00:15:24.569 --> 00:15:25.612
Jang Tae-sik.

00:15:26.530 --> 00:15:29.241
I'll make sure you don't commit
any more crimes in this life.

00:15:29.783 --> 00:15:30.784
We can't put

00:15:30.867 --> 00:15:33.328
more people in misery because of you.

00:15:34.663 --> 00:15:37.123
But don't you even dream
of going to heaven.

00:15:49.469 --> 00:15:51.930
- Yes?
- Han-young, you bastard!

00:15:52.013 --> 00:15:53.723
What bastard? Me?

00:15:53.974 --> 00:15:55.433
Yeah, you.

00:15:55.517 --> 00:15:57.561
How dare you scam me?

00:15:58.603 --> 00:16:00.063
You're dead.

00:16:02.107 --> 00:16:03.608
Prosecutor Park!

00:16:05.318 --> 00:16:07.070
The day I...

00:16:08.572 --> 00:16:11.157
Remember the day
I was robbed of my three billion won?

00:16:14.119 --> 00:16:16.621
You were pretty damn busy
with Mr. Lee, huh?

00:16:17.497 --> 00:16:19.082
CALL HISTORY

00:16:20.625 --> 00:16:22.961
You're dead, too, alright?

00:16:28.383 --> 00:16:29.426
Yes.

00:16:29.843 --> 00:16:33.388
The call history from you made
the world of a difference.

00:16:34.764 --> 00:16:36.766
Alright, looking forward to it.

00:16:44.399 --> 00:16:45.442
Lee Seong-dae has

00:16:45.525 --> 00:16:47.777
a record of everywhere we've been
and our call history

00:16:47.861 --> 00:16:49.446
around the time of the Miracle scam.

00:16:49.654 --> 00:16:52.574
What do we do now?
Sin-jin is going to catch on soon.

00:16:55.785 --> 00:16:56.786
Don't worry.

00:16:56.870 --> 00:16:58.663
Seong-dae and his greed will make him fall

00:16:58.747 --> 00:17:00.290
into yet another trap.

00:17:09.966 --> 00:17:13.678
So, how did that humble little party go
last time?

00:17:14.179 --> 00:17:16.139
- Did you have a good time?
- Were you there?

00:17:16.640 --> 00:17:17.974
No, well...

00:17:19.142 --> 00:17:21.561
Yeah, I went there
and went right back home.

00:17:22.479 --> 00:17:25.106
Isn't it about time
you introduce me to your friends?

00:17:25.857 --> 00:17:27.025
I don't have any.

00:17:27.776 --> 00:17:28.902
I didn't keep you hidden.

00:17:29.486 --> 00:17:31.237
I just had nobody to introduce you to.

00:17:31.321 --> 00:17:34.282
But you have friends,
you're just taking too long.

00:17:35.617 --> 00:17:36.618
There we go!

00:17:37.243 --> 00:17:38.286
I'm counting on you.

00:17:38.870 --> 00:17:39.871
Not for free.

00:17:40.872 --> 00:17:42.540
I get a wish, no questions asked.

00:17:42.624 --> 00:17:44.000
If you don't want that, just go.

00:17:46.044 --> 00:17:47.045
Okay, then.

00:17:47.253 --> 00:17:48.463
Fine.

00:17:48.546 --> 00:17:51.174
I'll do it. Just don't mess up.

00:17:55.345 --> 00:17:57.055
Han-young, you bastard.

00:17:57.681 --> 00:17:58.723
Have a seat.

00:18:01.643 --> 00:18:03.228
I see why Haenal's daughter

00:18:03.311 --> 00:18:05.980
came to that bullshit investment seminar.

00:18:07.482 --> 00:18:09.401
I heard you guys were getting married.

00:18:09.484 --> 00:18:11.319
What a match made in heaven, huh?

00:18:11.403 --> 00:18:14.114
Aw, are you already congratulating us?

00:18:16.032 --> 00:18:18.326
When did you clean up this office?

00:18:18.410 --> 00:18:20.412
Are you dumb

00:18:20.495 --> 00:18:22.163
or fearless?

00:18:24.666 --> 00:18:26.626
The police will look everywhere

00:18:27.460 --> 00:18:29.713
but not here again.

00:18:30.672 --> 00:18:31.840
Cheol-woo.

00:18:31.923 --> 00:18:33.091
We meet yet again.

00:18:36.094 --> 00:18:37.345
This is 500 million won.

00:18:39.806 --> 00:18:40.932
Just 500 million?

00:18:43.601 --> 00:18:45.562
Give me my three billion won back
right now.

00:18:45.937 --> 00:18:48.356
Or else, I take all of you down.

00:18:48.732 --> 00:18:50.650
I'll give you three billion in a week.

00:18:51.025 --> 00:18:53.570
That'll mean
that you have made 500 million.

00:18:53.987 --> 00:18:55.321
That's a good investment.

00:18:55.822 --> 00:18:58.199
You won't need to worry
about your daughter abroad now.

00:18:59.409 --> 00:19:00.869
Shut up, you bastard.

00:19:03.246 --> 00:19:04.664
You think I'll fall for it again?

00:19:04.748 --> 00:19:07.751
Join our firm once things settle.

00:19:08.543 --> 00:19:11.629
I know you're a Presiding Judge
at the Seoul Central Court.

00:19:11.713 --> 00:19:13.882
I'll give you an office with a good view.

00:19:15.049 --> 00:19:17.177
Not a bad offer
for keeping your mouth shut, huh?

00:19:18.720 --> 00:19:19.763
Shut it.

00:19:20.346 --> 00:19:21.890
You think I'll fall for it again?

00:19:21.973 --> 00:19:24.434
Give me back my three billion right now!

00:19:24.517 --> 00:19:25.685
Man.

00:19:26.436 --> 00:19:28.438
I told you. We don't have it right now!

00:19:31.941 --> 00:19:34.110
Better look for it, then.

00:19:36.446 --> 00:19:39.240
Shall I call Sin-jin right now?

00:19:43.912 --> 00:19:45.371
SENIOR PRESIDING JUDGE KANG SIN-JIN

00:19:47.499 --> 00:19:48.541
Wait.

00:19:49.250 --> 00:19:50.293
I'll give it to you now.

00:19:52.837 --> 00:19:55.632
You bastard. You don't even have the guts
to carry through it.

00:19:56.257 --> 00:19:57.717
The account number is

00:19:57.801 --> 00:20:00.136
236021069923

00:20:00.220 --> 00:20:02.680
for Ms. Lee Seon-yeong
at Gukje Bank, right?

00:20:02.806 --> 00:20:03.848
DEPOSIT AMOUNT: 0 WON

00:20:04.474 --> 00:20:05.558
Damn you!

00:20:05.725 --> 00:20:07.560
- Hold on.
- Wait a second.

00:20:07.852 --> 00:20:08.853
- Who the hell are you?
- Stop.

00:20:08.937 --> 00:20:10.730
How do you know
my daughter's bank account?

00:20:11.022 --> 00:20:13.566
Don't you lay a finger on him!

00:20:13.650 --> 00:20:14.776
She knows how to slap people!

00:20:14.859 --> 00:20:16.986
